Paper Wallet Generator

https://github.com/MethMatician/incakoinwalletgenerator

To change the image for the above wallet generator, right click on the image and save the image as style.png and place it near the IncaKoinWallet.html file.

After that, edit the IncaKoinWallet.html file, at line 7100 replace :

image = 'data:image/png;base64,i...(verylongline)........';

replace with

image="style.png";

now you can edit style.png.

This way you can change the picture, but you must rename and place the style.png manually each time.

But this way, what ever you add to the image

ie. denominations, information, links etc

will be added on the first printing, with no need to double print the paper.
